cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of medical imaging techniques, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a novel strategy for label fusion, which could be related to neural networks (cs.NE).
